      About this item

      • 【HD Stereo Sound Quality】The bluetooth karaoke machine is equipped with a 6.5” full frequency speaker and a 2.0” tweeter, adopting high and low pitch separation technology and professional reverberation adjustment function, which make the sound clearer, the bass stronger, the volume more moderate, and eliminate all the noise
      • 【Play in Multiple Ways】The karaoke machine for adults adopting Bluetooth 5.0 chip for high-speed and stable wireless transmission, with strong anti-interference and wider transmission range. Supports multiple playback methods such as Micro TF card, Flash USB, and AUX connection, and is compatible with Android phones, iPhones, iPads, tablets, and PCs.The remote control makes it easier and quicker to perform different functions
      • 【Six Color Lighting Modes】This karaoke speaker comes with colorful RGB lights and multiple lighting effects, allowing you to switch between different coloured lights at will. Built in 6500mAh high capacity battery, improves battery life and lasts for 8-10 hours without stopping. Enjoy the joy of the party with colorful lighting and wonderful music
      • 【Portable Karaoke Microphone】This party speaker can be carried in two ways, either by hand or by shoulder, and can be worn flexibly. The portable design is convenient for carrying and going out, and you can easily carry it to places such as beaches and outdoors. Experience the ultimate karaoke party outdoors with MOYLEAF portable bluetooth speaker
      • 【Desirable Option】The MOYLEAF speaker with microphone is equipped with a upgraded audio driver, providing clearer and more balanced sound quality, as well as 360 ° stereo surround sound effect. Immerse yourself in more powerful and shocking music. It is an ideal choice for beach parties, family gatherings, outdoor live streaming, and other occasions

          How customer reviews and ratings work

          Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

          To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

          Amazon Customer
          5 out of 5 stars
          I loved!
          I bought this karaoke machine mostly for my Galentine’s party and friends to use at home and we are very happy with it. The machine is good quality and easy to set up. It is lightweight which makes it very easy to carry around. It comes with two wireless microphones. The sound quality for the mics and the machine itself is great. We were easily able to pair it with our phones over Bluetooth to play our music directly through it. We have found a lot of karaoke songs on YouTube so that's what we normally use. It does come with a charging cable, but will charge with any USB Type C cable. You can even use your phone charger if you want! This karaoke machine is worth every penny and I highly recommend it to anyone who loves singing.

            1.0 out of 5 stars Mics and remote don’t work
            Reviewed in the United States on December 26, 2024
            Color: RedVerified Purchase
            It looks like this prime day purchase was a total fail and Santa should’ve tested the product before wrapping and delivering. Kids excitedly plugged the speaker in to charge then found our packages of brand new batteries for mics and remote Christmas morning. Batteries definitely worked as we tested them in other devices when neither mics nor remote would turn on at all. I found a plug-in mic that we already owned and it didn’t work with the device either so I have no idea if the speaker does more than light up and hum. Only a couple sound effects buttons worked and that was only a couple of the times that we tried them (they didn’t try most attempts.) Oh and mics are cheap plastic. There is no way this is almost $1k full price as advertised – the sale price appears to be more like a mark-up. Signed, a very disappointed mom of 4 kids that’s supposed to be hosting a Karaoke party tonight…

            5.0 out of 5 stars Amazing!!
            Reviewed in the United States on January 5, 2025
            Color: RedVerified Purchase
            We have been looking for a small practical karaoke machine to have around family gatherings to pass the time. Once we got this speaker we loved it! The only issue was that i would not connect to out iPhones or ipads. We really wanted a karaoke machine that we could take anywhere like the park, friends house etc so not being able to connect put phones with it was a real inconvenience. We decided to exchange it for the same product. There was no issue with returning it and we got out replacement speaker super fast. Upon opening it we immediately rushed to see if it would connect to our phones and it did! We love this product and have used it almost every weekend. The microphones work seemingly and feel like they are very well made. The speaker is relatively easy to connect and if you dont want to use it as a karaoke machine you can just use it as a regular speaker and the volume is perfect you dont need something super loud to have a good time. Any who definitely worth the cost!
